OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain breezy in the north tonight
OL,7,Fwith a few showers. Elsewhere it will
OL,8,Fbecome generally dry and clear, with
OL,9,Fthe wind falling light. A few mist or
OL,10,Ffog patches forming, and turning
OL,11,Ffrosty in some rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FEarly frost and fog clearing
OL,14,Fto leave plenty of sunshine on Sunday
OL,15,Fmorning. Cloud bubbling up during the
OL,16,Fday, and there will be a few showers,
OL,17,Fmainly in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
